South African-born Master KG has people around the globe dancing to his hit track 'Jerusalema'. JOHANNESBURG - Jerusalema hitmaker, Master KG has won the Best African Act at the 2020 MTV EMAs. In a short clip posted on Twitter, Master KG thanked his fans for all their support. READ: Master KG continues to break barriers with Jerusalema "I would like to thank and every single person out there, all over the world for making this possible," he said. "I just won Best African Act at the MTV EMA 2020 and I would like to thank my sister, Nomcebo, my team, Open Mic Productions and everyone who is behind Master KG, thank you guys so much. Jerusalema captured the hearts of millions of people around the world. It resulted in the dance challenge going viral with people around the globe sending videos of themselves jiving to the tune.